Description:
Deals &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[DamageTable.OH_Shield_Attack_Bash.DmgCoef * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; &lt;img src="lyshineui/images/icons/tooltip/icon_tooltip_strike_opaque" xPadding="4" scale="1.7" yOffset="4"&gt;&lt;/img&gt;weapon damage, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;staggering&lt;/font&gt; and &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;stunning&lt;/font&gt; foes in front of you for &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[Type_StatusEffectData.Sword_ShieldBash_Stun2.BaseDuration]}s&lt;/font&gt;. 

This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.) 

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your sword, this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.OH_Shield_Attack_Bash.TauntDuration]}s to all enemies hit. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;

For &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;8s&lt;/font&gt;, &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;reduce&lt;/font&gt; the incoming base &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;damage&lt;/font&gt; from attackers by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SwordAbilityTable.Ability_Sword_FinalStand.BaseDamageReduction * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt; and reduce the attacker's &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;stamina damage&lt;/font&gt; while blocking by &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;{[SwordAbilityTable.Ability_Sword_FinalStand.BlockDamageReduction * 100]}%&lt;/font&gt;. 


This ability has &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_SemiBold.font" color="#ffd45f"&gt;grit&lt;/font&gt;. &lt;font face="lyshineui/fonts/Nimbus_Regular_Italic.font" color="#828282"&gt;(Grit prevents you from being staggered by incoming attacks.)

Taunt Gem Compatible: If you have a Carnelian gem equipped in your sword, activating this ability inflicts taunt for {[DamageTable.OH_Shield_FinalStand.TauntDuration]}s to all enemies within 8m. (Taunt causes monsters to focus only on you.)&lt;/font&gt;
